Short answer: No.<br /><br />Long answer: Maybe something could dump roms by playing sound (like tapedump on the NES), or showing video patterns.  TV capture software could take it over then.  But you'd need to run your own custom code, and there's probably better ways of dumping roms than this.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=53">Dwedit</a> — Tue Feb 28, 2012 10:51 pm</p><hr />
